  ('dietitian-moex-02266', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-106-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '以下是某食品的部分營養標示內容，其中容易增加心血管疾病風險的成分是那些？ NUTRITION FACTS Serving Size 1 Tbsp (14 g) Servings 1 Amount Per Serving Calories 100  Calories from Fat 100 % Daily Value*', '["Saturated Fat 2.5 g  12%", "Trans Fat 2.5 g  ……", "Cholesterol 30 mg  10%", "Protein 0 g  0%  ⑤"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "58527587a09e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2294967d91a8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-02267', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-106-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '食品中所存在的反式脂肪酸，主要是由食品在加工的過程中，脂肪酸發生何種化學變化？', '["飽和脂肪酸進行過氧化作用轉變而來", "飽和脂肪酸進行氫化作用轉變而來", "多元不飽和脂肪酸進行過氧化作用而來", "多元不飽和脂肪酸進行氫化作用而來"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "58527587a09e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2294967d91a8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-02268', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-106-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關食物中脂肪酸的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["碳數大於12者為長鏈脂肪酸，消化吸收後，由淋巴系統運送", "椰子油或棕櫚油所含之脂肪酸，碳數大多落在6至16間之不飽和脂肪酸", "奶油、全脂奶等乳製品所含之脂肪酸，碳數大多落在4至24間之飽和脂肪酸", "脂肪酸的吸收率，不論碳數長短，均比葡萄糖慢"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "58527587a09e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2294967d91a8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-02269', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-106-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '在飢餓時，體內脂肪的主要功能，下列何者錯誤？', '["甘油進行gluconeogenesis，合成葡萄糖", "脂肪酸進行β-oxidation作用，在葡萄糖充足下進行TCA循環", "脂肪酸進行β-oxidation作用，在葡萄糖不足的情況下進行ketogenesis", "脂肪酸進行β-oxidation作用，在葡萄糖不足的情況下進行gluconeogenesis，合成葡萄糖"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "58527587a09e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2294967d91a8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-02270', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-106-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關膽固醇的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["對多數人而言，體內膽固醇約三分之二是自行生合成，僅三分之一來自食物", "是細胞膜和胞器膜的重要組成分", "是植物固醇", "是合成雌激素（estrogen）和睪固酮（testosterone）的原料"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "58527587a09e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2294967d91a8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-02271', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-106-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那些生理現象是厭食症（anorexia nervosa）和暴食症（bulimia nervosa）共有的症狀？①缺鐵性貧血', '["免疫功能下降", "胃潰瘍", "無月經症", "血鉀失衡"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "58527587a09e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2294967d91a8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-02272', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-106-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '以低熱量飲食減肥經過一段時間後，體重會停滯不動，不容易繼續下降，下列何者與此情況無直接相關？', '["可能是因為體脂肪所釋放的有害物質（toxins）擾亂體內的新陳代謝及內分泌功能所致", "可能是因為在減重過程中體脂肪減少，引起身體調整新陳代謝速率，不讓體重下降之故", "可增加身體活動量例如運動，以提高基礎代謝率來克服此情況", "此種情況就是所謂的「yo-yo effect」"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "58527587a09e", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2294967d91a8", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第一次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
